ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.plugin.impl

Class BusinessApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revolsys.properties.BaseObjectWithProperties
      • ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.plugin.impl.BusinessApplication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.revolsys.properties.ObjectWithProperties, Comparable<BusinessApplication>

    public class BusinessApplication
extends com.revolsys.properties.BaseObjectWithProperties
implements Comparable<BusinessApplication>
    The BusinessApplication describes a business application which can be invoked via the CPF. It contains all the metadata to generate a capabilities document for the service and for the CPF to be able to invoke the application.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    paustin
